    scene expression 'background/BG_06A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "---But I can't just leave in the middle of class."
    
    "\"...... Please.\""
    
    "I bring my hands together and pray silently that she won't start any \"interesting\" trouble for twenty minutes."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_06A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Class ends."
    
    "I dash out of the classroom engulfed in the lunchtime commotion."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_11A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "I bolt down through the hallway."
    
    ".... Arcueid is out back."
    
    "Because it's lunchtime, there may be one or two students going there."
    
    "Before that, I have to send her away from school....!"
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_04.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "I pant with exertion."
    
    "I exit the hallway and out into the courtyard."
    
    "Fortunately, no one else has gone outside."
    
    "All that's left is to grab Arcueid, but.."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "\".... The worst.\""
    
    "Entering the back of the school, I unthinkingly voice my thoughts."
    
    "In the back,"
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T07.png' as i0 at fgpos(-28, 0)
    
    "I can see a very hostile Arcueid and.."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T07.png' as i0 at fgpos(-28, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/CEL_T07A.png' as i1 at fgpos(116, 0)
    
    "through the worst twist of fate, Ciel-senpai is also present."
    
    "As if facing an invader, Senpai is staring at Arcueid."
    
    "\"Arcueid....!\""
    
    "Both of them turn around."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T06.png' as i0 at fgpos(-28, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/CEL_T07A.png' as i1 at fgpos(116, 0)
    
    "\"Shiki.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T06.png' as i0 at fgpos(-28, 0)
    
    show expression 'foreground/CEL_T06A.png' as i1 at fgpos(116, 0)
    
    "\"-------\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    ".... Thank goodness."
    
    "Arcueid's hostility seems to fade."
    
    "After looking back at Arcueid, Senpai leaves in another direction."
    
    "\"Ah.... Senpai.\""
    
    "She must've been offended by being glared at by Arcueid."
    
    "For Senpai to just disappear like that without saying anything must mean something."
    
    "\"Arcueid, you....!\""
    
    "I run over to her."
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T16.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Shiki you slowpoke!\""
    
    "She yells at me as I get to her."
    
    "\"Hey.... slow?"
    
    "Hey now.\""
    
    "\"But weren't you?"
    
    "I know you saw me, but you never came down."
    
    "If you came earlier, I wouldn't have been seen by that person!\""
    
    ".... \"That person\" must mean Senpai."
    
    "\"It couldn't be helped, I have my circumstances."
    
    "I'm different from you, I'm just a normal student."
    
    "In the first place, why the heck did you come here?\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"I just felt something from around here."
    
    "Then I picked up your scent and realized it was your school.\""
    
    "\".... So you weren't thinking and you just came for no reason?\""
    
    "I give a frown."
    
    "Is she a dog or something?"
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T04.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Well excuse me!"
    
    "I came here for a reason."
    
    "There's hardly any traces of The Dead here, so I wanted to see it for myself.\""
    
    "\"Really?"
    
    "But if there's no traces of The Dead here, then shouldn't this place be unimportant?"
    
    "There's no one at school at night, so if The Dead wanted some prey, they would go downtown, not to a school.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T10.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\".... Well, that does make sense.\""
    
    "\"There's nothing strange here."
    
    "I can't really sense The Dead, but since my eyes see death, I can tell without taking off my glasses.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T06.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"I see."
    
    "If you say so, Shiki, then there's nothing strange about this place, perhaps.\""
    
    "\"Not 'perhaps', definitely.\""
    
    "Arcueid looks like she doesn't believe me."
    
    "\"Anyway, if we stay here any longer, people will see us."
    
    "I'll keep my promise for sure, so just go home and rest."
    
    "We may see the 'enemy' tonight.\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    show expression 'foreground/ARK_T03.png' as i0 at fgpos(36, 0)
    
    "\"Oh?"
    
    "You sound like you want me out of here, Shiki?\""
    
    "She starts to look angry again."
    
    "\"Ah, that's just your imagination, so hurry on back."
    
    "Otherwise things might get a little hairy.\""
    
    "Go, go."
    
    "I push her from behind."
    
    "\"............\""
    
    scene expression 'background/BG_05A.jpg' at bgpos
    
    "Though her eyes indicate she wants to say something, she just leaves silently."
    
    "\".... Man."
    
    "If I see Senpai, I have to apologize to her about Arcueid.\""
    
    "Thinking aloud, I go back."
    
    scene expression 'background/IMA_10.jpg' at bgpos
    
